Name: Putra
Phrase: Aduhduhduh..

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Everybody, you hurt?

Name: Putra
Phrase: I'm fine.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: I managed to...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: GHHH!?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Queensway, what's wrong?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: I think I hurt my leg, I sprained when I was cushioning Paddington...

Name: Paddington
Phrase: Hawawa! I-I'm so sorry! If only I was a bit lighter, this wouldn't have happened...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: No, I don't think Miss Paddington's weight is that relevant. Are you injured?

Name: Paddington
Phrase: I'm fine here! I'm perfectly healthy from my toes to the top of my head!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Then that's good to hear, because you've done a great job this time, Miss Paddington. I'm sure we'll need your help too on the way out.

Name: Paddington
Phrase: Hwawa, I'm in love with you when you put it like that!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Eh? No, you know...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: I-It's a knight's duty to protect the Divine Children after all!

Name: Amiens
Phrase: But it's quite a blow that Mademoiselle Queensway got injured here. It will be difficult to cut through the enemy camp like before.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: My apologies. But I can still participate in combat. It may be difficult to move quickly, however...

Name: Amiens
Phrase: No problem. If push comes to shove, I'll run with Queensway on my back! If that's not possible, we can take the minecart and make a run for it.

Name: Putra
Phrase: I wonder if there are even minecarts at this lower level.

Name: Rouen
Phrase: Heheheh, of course... there are!

Name: Putra
Phrase: Huh?

Name: Rouen
Phrase: For I have found it.

Name: Putra
Phrase: No, about that, anyone can find this one. This one's big.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Amazing. It's bigger than the minecarts I saw up there...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: It's got proper rails on it too. Maybe we can ascend upwards on this cart?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: It would be possible if there was a powerful power source, like the carts that just came crashing in from below. We've already come this far in search of that power source...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Perhaps the device here is to generate energy.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: But we don't know how to operate it at all. We really require someone like Miss Yoshino to handle a machine like this...

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Let's not touch anything for now. In any case, we'll have to find Yoshino and Yakutsk before we can escape. We have to think about meeting up with those two first.

Name: Putra
Phrase: They said they were going to find a way out. Will the two be sneaking through narrow places again?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: They've said something about floorboards, so it's likely they won't be using stairs or lifts.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Even if they were to successfully avoid that minecart hell, I wonder if they'd know where we were.

Name: Paddington
Phrase: About that! I've got an idea!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Paddington, you're on a roll today. What's your good idea?

Name: Paddington
Phrase: Yes! That would be to...

Name: Paddington
Phrase: Blow the whistle!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: The whistle...

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: I see, if we blow this as hard as we can, maybe Yakutsk and her will hear us!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: We can let them know where we are!

Name: Putra
Phrase: Vivienne, let's try blowing it.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Oui, blow twice for 'requesting reinforcements'...
Believing that Yakutsk and Yoshino had escaped safely and were looking for them, Vivienne blew her whistle without hesitation.
The sound of the whistle calling for her friends echoes through the silent lowest levels of the ruins of Ouvrage Schoenenbourg.
Intruder Alert. Intruder Alert.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Feels like, you've called someone else instead?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Apparently so.
Intruders Have Entered The Power Room. Radio Operator To Discard All Records.

Name: Maginot Cannon
Phrase: Furthermore, I Will Destroy The Intruders. I Will Eliminate The Enemy As Soon As Possible And Return To Defensive Duty.

Name: Putra
Phrase: That's not a person!

Name: Paddington
Phrase: Hawawa! Something very scary's here!

Name: Putra
Phrase: That's a cannon, right? Is that a hidden weapon in this fortress or something?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Cannons neither talk nor walk!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: A self-supporting fortress artillery... It's rare to find an ancient weapon that remains in such perfect condition.

Name: Amiens
Phrase: Wow~ a self-supporting fortress artillery is too cool! I wonder how it works?

Name: Rouen
Phrase: If I were to name that cannon, it'll be...

Name: Amiens
Phrase: Automatic fortress artillery!

Name: Rouen
Phrase: Self-supporting running cannon!

Name: Paddington
Phrase: Nah, it's simply 'self-propelled artillery'!

Name: Amiens & Rouen
Phrase: C'est ça!

Name: Maginot Cannon
Phrase: As The Defender Of Maginot, I Will Eliminate You. I Will Not Let You Proceed Beyond The Maginot Line.

Name: Maginot Cannon
Phrase: Maginot, Engagé.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Does it mean it's really going to attack? Or is the name of this machine called Maginot?

Name: Maginot Cannon
Phrase: MAGINOT, ATTAQUEEEEEEE!!

Name: Putra
Phrase: Wha...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Th-there's a big hole in the wall?

Name: Putra
Phrase: That Maginot's no joke! If that thing hit us directly, we'll be nothing but ashes left!

Name: Maginot Cannon
Phrase: Maginot Will Not Miss For Real Next Time.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: It reloads fast! It'll fire again soon! Spread out!

Name: Maginot Cannon
Phrase: Targeting Slowest Enemy!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: It's targeting Queensway who's immobile! Rouen, do something!

Name: Rouen
Phrase: I'm on it! Activating Sacred Holy Shield!

Name: Putra
Phrase: You're going to use magic to block it!? That's absurd! You can't stop that shot!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Non, Rouen should be able to do it...

Name: Maginot Cannon
Phrase: MAGINOOOT, CANOOOON!

Name: Rouen
Phrase: HOLY ANGEL SAINT-SEVER! MAY THOU PROTECT ME!

Name: Rouen
Phrase: Kuhuhuhuh... See now? Witness the power of the Holy Angel.

Name: Rouen
Phrase: Kuhuhuh... Cough...

Name: Amiens
Phrase: ROUEN!

Name: Rouen
Phrase: T-that was... kinda reckless indeed. But, I did save her from one shot...

Name: Amiens
Phrase: Yes, I was watching you. Rouen, you're still amazing.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Are you kidding me? You seriously blocked it...

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Rouen is one of the best mages in the Verforet Gendarmerie. Unlike me, who only uses flashy offensive magic, she is able to use a wide range of magic. Even if I unleash my magic at full power, Rouen should be able to negate it.

Name: Amiens
Phrase: Before I get to know Rouen, she was already exploring ancient ruins all by herself. Unless exceptional in handling magic, it's unlikely that a little girl would be able to explore the ruins alone.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: But the next one is very unlikely to be blockable again. If I am targeted, you all have to go around and take the flanks. You won't stand a chance if you engage head on. Aim for its legs and stagger its stance.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Sure, if we break its legs, we have a chance to win. But I don't think it will work so well if we bait its attack towards Queensway...

Name: Maginot Cannon
Phrase: The Maginot Is The Impenetratable Defence Line. No One Can Break It.

Name: Maginot Cannon
Phrase: QUOI!?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Gun shots!?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Where the heck did that come from...

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Queensway, Putra, look up.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Up?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: There's a fox tail hanging from the ceiling...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: That's Miss Yoshino!

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Did you see that? Did you see that Yoshino, I hit it with this weird gun! I wonder if I'll ever be a sniper like Volgo someday?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Ooooh, saw that clearly. It doesn't seem to be working at all.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: But most importantly, we need to get down below as soon as possible now that the teki knows we're here.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: That's because your ass is stuck again, no? Enough of this. I'm going to kick you off the ceiling.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: That would be great. Can't get out anyway.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: EISENGRADIAN KIIICK!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Oooooh-, just behind the target too...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: ...and while pretending to be a dolt, attack mercilessly!

Name: Maginot Cannon
Phrase: Are You Serious!?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yakutsk, Come'on!

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: DON'T HAFTA TELL ME!

Name: Maginot Cannon
Phrase: MAGINOOOOOOO!?

Name: Maginot Cannon
Phrase: Why Did You Have Our Army's MAS-36...?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Oh, this? I picked it up because it was on the floor. I thought it would be good for breaking the grating on the ducts.

Name: Maginot Cannon
Phrase: MAMAMAMAMAM!? Use Weapons The Right Way!

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Right back at ya. Look at yourself in the mirror before you say that.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Sou, sou, fortress cannons don't walk the walk and they don't talk the talk.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Girls! We've reduced its mobility! Now it's just a resilient but slow fortress cannon. Let's surround and destroy it!

Name: Putra
Phrase: Actually aiming the lower half of the body... That's really relentless.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: But this makes our job easier, we can cover Queensway and Rouen while we fight.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Yakutsk, Yoshino, how nice to have you back! I love you both so much!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Oooh-, this all really feels so embarrassing to hear.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: This sure looks pretty heated up. Let her touch your tail a lot later.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Verforet doesn't need steel weapons. I'll melt those junk right away with my magic!
